My daughter's been crazy for Barney ever since a neighbor unloading her old toys on us gave us one of their old DVDs. I usually just get Barney DVDs from the library, and I find that my daughter goes nuts for some of them and isn't much interested in the others. This one is hands down her favorite - I like it too, it contains a lot of useful exercise, hygiene, nutrition, "you're growing" information and fun songs and information about going to the doctor and the dentist. This is one of the few that we get from the library that I felt like I needed to go out and buy to have around. Definitely worthwhile!
